name: Pixel Art E.T
description: This E.T is called Mavruux, he's the captain of the spaceship Tezota, he and his crew coming from a planet called Tezoz. Since he left his planet to go seeking for livable planet arround Tezoz, Mavruux has become very sick, he can't stop coughing virus and spreading snot everywhere in the spaceship. This is not inaugurating well for the mission, plus, the other members of the crew are really scare of catching this virus unknown by the E.T species at this time. Mavruux has a wife and two young Tezotien children, he prays not to die during this mission to see his family again one day.
